title: Ndox Electrique - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Ndox Electrique performing live at the Conservatoire de Rennes 
Auditorium in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2023. Recorded December 5, 2023. 

Songs:
Lëk Ndau Mbay
Ngor Diouf Ya Demon
He Yay Naliné
Indi Mewmi
Rakad (Sabar Improvisation)
Ngor Diouf Né Du Wallé
Sam Sa Nga Mboro

François R. Cambuzat - Guitar, Vocals, Computer
Gianna Greco - Bass, Vocals
Ndeye Coumba Mbaye Kebe - Vocals
Awa Mbodji - Vocals
Oumar Ngom - Sabar, Vocals
Mamadou "Pape" Ngom - Percussion, Sabar, Vocals
Mouhamet "Sangue" Sambe - Percussion, Sabar, Vocals

Audio Engineer: Matt Ogaz
Guest Audio Engineer: Alessandro Maffeifei
Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro, Scott Holpainen
Editor: Scott Holpainen
